Description_lang: Balls of garbage emerge beneath up to $465344s1 players, allowing them to control the ball's movement and roll over small enemies and garbage piles to absorb them.After absorbing enough, the ball increases in size and can absorb even larger objects.
AuraDescription_lang: You are a nigh-unstoppable sphere of pure garbage. Roll up objects in your path to increase in size!Damage taken reduced by $s2%.
